SEW: Sewing and mending fabric goods

Category: Domestic
Base skill: 40% (+5%/level, cap 98%)

Sewing, mending, and making clothing and other fabric goods by hand.
Useful for patching worn gear, tailoring clothing, or making a
living as a seamstress or tailor.

NOTES:
  No AetherMUD command currently rolls this skill directly. It is
  available for character concept and staff-adjudicated roleplay.

